data.description: 827 Killian Hill is ready for your personal touches! Award winning schools, easy access to shopping, dining, and everything else that Lilburn and Cedar Creek Estates (with optional pool & tennis membership) has to offer. This 3 bedroom, 2 full bath each features spacious living and dining areas, updated kitchen with granite countertops and stainless appliances with breakfast area, and laminate floors. There is also an unfinished basement that provides for endless opportunities to create a game room or in-law/tee suite. On almost half an acre, you can sit on the screened back porch and enjoy your private backyard oasis with gas connection perfect for grilling. Schedule your showing today!
